data.description:
ALL BRICK!!! PRICED IS RIGHT!! This home is waiting for you! Come see this gorgeous 3 bedroom 1.5 Bath with HUGE den. New LPV flooring in Livingroom, hallway and all bedrooms. From the front door, walk into a naturally sun lit Livingroom then turn down the hall to a kitchen that's perfect for cooking your family meals. Right off the kitchen is a lovely dining area that flows into a huge den that features a beautiful wood burning fireplace and Oversized Laundry room.
 Master bedroom has its own 1/2 bathroom and the two other bedrooms are just the perfect size.  Fully gated large backyard with storage shed!  priced "AS IS"
